Bombay Sandwich Recipe
1) Spread butter, then green chutney on the bread
2) Add Layer boiled potato slices, onion, tomato, and cucumber
3) Sprinkle black pepper
Green Chutney Recipe: Blend fresh coriander, mint leaves, green chilies, garlic, ginger, lemon juice, salt, and a little water to a smooth paste.
Optional: You can add cheese & grill for a toasty twist!
Enjoy
